name: EliasEkonFu's DePaul Utopia Interactive
description: Welcome to EliasEkonFu's Utopia Interactive! This program is a clickable walk around and interactable map around the campus of DePaul University. Click on doors and arrows to move around to different rooms and other locations. Be sure to move the mouse around the entire screen! You might find some cool sound playing objects and popups. Enjoy! :)
